NIGDE NEMA.

26
00:02:47,751 --> 00:02:51,381
UPLAŠIO SI GA SVOJOM GOVORANCIJOM,
JE L', STAMENKO?

27
00:02:52,881 --> 00:02:54,091
ŠTA RADIŠ, ŠMRKAVKO?

28
00:02:54,341 --> 00:02:55,761
SAD ÆE ONA POBEDITI.

29
00:02:55,801 --> 00:02:58,301
ONA JE MOJA PRINCEZA.
ŠTA POŽELI, TO DOBIJE.

30
00:02:58,345 --> 00:03:01,465
KAMENOGLAVA?
ZAR NIJE POKUŠALA ŽIVOG DA TE SAHRANI?

31
00:03:01,515 --> 00:03:02,645
SAMO NA NEKOLIKO SATI.

32
00:03:05,185 --> 00:03:09,145
ZMAJEVI SU NAM NEKAD
PREDSTAVLJALI PROBLEM,

33
00:03:09,189 --> 00:03:10,609
ALI TO JE BILO PRE PET GODINA.

34
00:03:10,649 --> 00:03:14,939
SADA ŽIVE S NAMA.
PA, ZAŠTO I NE BI?

35
00:03:14,987 --> 00:03:16,907
IMAMO ZMAJARNIKE PO MERI,

36
00:03:16,947 --> 00:03:19,117
HRANILIŠTA "JEDI KOLIKO MOŽEŠ",

37
00:03:19,157 --> 00:03:21,487
KOMPLETNU USLUGU PRANJA ZMAJEVA,

38
00:03:23,078 --> 00:03:26,828
ÈAK I VRHUNSKU ZAŠTITU OD POŽARA,
AKO SMEM TAKO DA KAŽEM.

39
00:03:28,167 --> 00:03:29,667
VREME JE, ŽDERONJO.

40
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,290
NEG' ŠTA. POSLEDNJI KRUG!

41
00:03:36,049 --> 00:03:38,049
CRNA OVCA!
BRŽE, LETEÆI BESU.

42
00:03:38,093 --> 00:03:39,843
JOŠ MOŽEMO DA POBEDIMO!

43
00:03:42,181 --> 00:03:43,641
HAJDE, BLJUCE!
-IDEMO!

44
00:03:44,641 --> 00:03:45,601
BRŽE, MESOŽDERE!

45
00:03:47,477 --> 00:03:49,437
BRZO! BRZO! BRŽE!

46
00:03:50,397 --> 00:03:51,857
TVOJ VELIKI TRENUTAK.

47
00:03:52,399 --> 00:03:53,939
ŽELIM TI LEP LET!

48
00:03:57,321 --> 00:03:58,321
DIŽI SE! GORE!

49
00:04:01,950 --> 00:04:03,240
NE!
-DA!

50
00:04:03,285 --> 00:04:04,745
ODLIÈNO IZVEDENO, MESOŽDERE.

51
00:04:05,704 --> 00:04:08,124
IZVOLI, DRAGA.
MOJA VREDI DESET POENA.

52
00:04:08,665 --> 00:04:10,205
DA! CRNA OVCA!

53
00:04:11,877 --> 00:04:13,957
NADMEÆETE SE ZA KAMENOGLAVU?

54
00:04:14,004 --> 00:04:15,304
TOTALNO POBEÐUJEM!

55
00:04:15,339 --> 00:04:16,759
POBEÐUJEMO ZAJEDNO!

56
00:04:17,925 --> 00:04:18,975
NE!

57
00:04:21,637 --> 00:04:23,257
SAD NIKO NE MOŽE DA ME ZAUSTAVI!

58
00:04:23,305 --> 00:04:25,935
OSIM MENE.
POVEZANI SMO, GENIJALKO.

59
00:04:25,974 --> 00:04:28,484
PRESTANI DA MI KRADEŠ SVU SLAVU!
-HEJ!

60
00:04:29,728 --> 00:04:30,768
SREDI IH, ASTRID!

61
00:04:30,812 --> 00:04:33,192
TO JE MOJA SLAVA!
-UVEK SVE POKVARIŠ!

62
00:04:33,232 --> 00:04:34,272
BEZ OVCE, NEMA SLAVE!

63
00:04:34,316 --> 00:04:35,316
MOJA SI!

64
00:04:37,194 --> 00:04:38,244
ASTRID!

65
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:39,648
DOBAR POTEZ!

66
00:04:40,906 --> 00:04:43,616
TO JE MOJA BUDUÆA SNAJKA!

67
00:04:47,621 --> 00:04:48,541
IZVINI!

68
00:04:48,580 --> 00:04:49,370
LETEÆI BESU!

69
00:05:01,885 --> 00:05:05,305
TO JE 13! ASTRID JE POBEDILA!

70
00:05:07,432 --> 00:05:10,562
DA, BERK JE SKORO SAVRŠEN.

71
00:05:10,602 --> 00:05:12,062
ISPLATIO SE SAV MOJ TRUD.

72
00:05:12,437 --> 00:05:17,187
SJAJNO JE I ZATO ŠTO
ZA VIKINGA NA LEÐIMA ZMAJA,

73
00:05:17,234 --> 00:05:19,614
SVET ODJEDNOM POSTAJE MNOGO VEÆI.

74
00:05:36,879 --> 00:05:37,919
TO!

75
